====Derived terms====
〆 is primarily used as an abbreviation for 締 (sometimes 閉), in 締める (〆る), 締切 (〆切), and [[締高]] (〆高). Another rarer use is 〆粕, (for 搾め糟, [[しめかす]]), and there is also occasional use of 乄, as in 乄高.

